  DSX --> HBL

  ASSETS -->|"bannertool<br/>makebanner + makesmdh"| CIABUILD
  ELF -->|"makerom<br/>uses .elf + .bnr + .icn"| CIABUILD
  CIABUILD --> CIA
  CIA --> INSTALL
  INSTALL --> MENU

